"platforms/mac/logging\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1281: \"gateway/logging\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1282: \"logging\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1341: \"nodes/audio\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1344: \"nodes/voicewake\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1402: \"cli/voicecall\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1749: \"zh-CN/plugins/voice-call\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1776: \"zh-CN/nodes/audio\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1779: \"zh-CN/nodes/voicewake\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1849: \"zh-CN/platforms/mac/voicewake\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1850: \"zh-CN/platforms/mac/voice-overlay\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1856: \"zh-CN/platforms/mac/logging\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1884: \"zh-CN/gateway/logging\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1932: \"pages\": [\"zh-CN/network\", \"zh-CN/logging\"]\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:1995: \"zh-CN/cli/voicecall\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\index.md:86: Send and receive images, audio, and documents.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\index.md:92: Pair iOS and Android nodes for Canvas, camera, and voice-enabled workflows.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:2: summary: \"Logging overview: file logs, console output, CLI tailing, and the Control UI\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:4: - You need a beginner-friendly overview of logging\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:7: title: \"Logging Overview\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:10: # Logging\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:32: \"logging\": {\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:97: Console formatting is controlled by `logging.consoleStyle`.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:99: ## Configuring logging\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:101: All logging configuration lives under `logging` in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:105: \"logging\": {\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:118: - `logging.level`: **file logs** (JSONL) level.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:119: - `logging.consoleLevel`: **console** verbosity level.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:127: `logging.consoleStyle`:\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:137: - `logging.redactSensitive`: `off` | `tools` (default: `tools`)\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:138: - `logging.redactPatterns`: list of regex strings to override the default set\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:162: volume can be high; keep `logging.level` and exporter filters in mind.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:201: Use flags to turn on extra, targeted debug logs without raising `logging.level`.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:220: - Flag logs go to the standard log file (same as `logging.file`).\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:221: - Output is still redacted according to `logging.redactSensitive`.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:262: - Traces/metrics can be toggled with `traces` / `metrics` (default: on). Traces\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:338: - `diagnostics.otel.logs` enables OTLP log export for the main logger output.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:342: - OTLP logs use the same structured records written to `logging.file`.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:343: - Respect `logging.level` (file log level). Console redaction does **not** apply\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:351: in `logging.file`.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\logging.md:352: - **Need more detail?** Set `logging.level` to `debug` or `trace` and retry.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:63: �   ��� logger.ts                  # Subsystem logger\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:292: The system prompt is built in `buildAgentSystemPrompt()` (`system-prompt.ts`). It assembles a full prompt with sections including Tooling, Tool Call Style, Safety guardrails, OpenClaw CLI reference, Skills, Docs, Workspace, Sandbox, Messaging, Reply Tags, Voice, Silent Replies, Heartbeats, Runtime metadata, plus Memory and Reactions when enabled, and optional context files and extra system prompt content. Sections are trimmed for minimal prompt mode used by subagents.\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:441: Reply directives like `[[media:url]]`, `[[voice]]`, `[[reply:id]]` are parsed and extracted:\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\pi.md:444: const { text: cleanedText, mediaUrls, audioAsVoice, replyToId } = consumeReplyDirectives(chunk);\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:2: summary: \"Text-to-speech (TTS) for outbound replies\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tts.md:4: - Enabling text-to-speech for replies"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":237,"aggregated":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:300: \"source\": \"/audio\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:301: \"destination\": \"/nodes/audio\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:524: \"source\": \"/mac/logging\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:525: \"destination\": \"/platforms/mac/logging\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:556: \"source\": \"/mac/voice-overlay\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:557: \"destination\": \"/platforms/mac/voice-overlay\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:560: \"source\": \"/mac/voicewake\",\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\docs.json:561: \"destination\": \"/platforms/mac/voicewake\"\r\nC:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\n