{"type":"message","id":"48ad74cd","parentId":"2e2c0390","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:03:37.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Voy a activar la transcripción de audio en la config, luego reinicio el gateway para que tome el cambio y probamos.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c334648d1481918718c137066b5b2b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_mExoWXLeS4bEmLZyGOGkccuS|fc_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c3346cb6e88191a3fe3df1104ced19","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","old_string":"  \"tools\": {\n    \"profile\": \"coding\",\n    \"agentToAgent\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"allow\": [\n        \"ares\",\n        \"prometeo\",\n        \"hestia\",\n        \"main\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"sessions\": {\n      \"visibility\": \"all\"\n    },\n    \"web\": {\n      \"search\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\"\n      }\n    }\n  },","new_string":"  \"tools\": {\n    \"profile\": \"coding\",\n    \"agentToAgent\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"allow\": [\n        \"ares\",\n        \"prometeo\",\n        \"hestia\",\n        \"main\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"sessions\": {\n      \"visibility\": \"all\"\n    },\n    \"web\": {\n      \"search\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"media\": {\n      \"audio\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"provider\": \"openai\",\n            \"model\": \"gpt-4o-mini-transcribe\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\openclaw.json\",\"old_string\":\"  \\\"tools\\\": {\\n    \\\"profile\\\": \\\"coding\\\",\\n    \\\"agentToAgent\\\": {\\n      \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n      \\\"allow\\\": [\\n        \\\"ares\\\",\\n        \\\"prometeo\\\",\\n        \\\"hestia\\\",\\n        \\\"main\\\"\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    \\\"sessions\\\": {\\n      \\\"visibility\\\": \\\"all\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"web\\\": {\\n      \\\"search\\\": {\\n        \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n        \\\"provider\\\": \\\"duckduckgo\\\"\\n      }\\n    }\\n  },\",\"new_string\":\"  \\\"tools\\\": {\\n    \\\"profile\\\": \\\"coding\\\",\\n    \\\"agentToAgent\\\": {\\n      \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n      \\\"allow\\\": [\\n        \\\"ares\\\",\\n        \\\"prometeo\\\",\\n        \\\"hestia\\\",\\n        \\\"main\\\"\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    \\\"sessions\\\": {\\n      \\\"visibility\\\": \\\"all\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"web\\\": {\\n      \\\"search\\\": {\\n        \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n        \\\"provider\\\": \\\"duckduckgo\\\"\\n      }\\n    },\\n    \\\"media\\\": {\\n      \\\"audio\\\": {\\n        \\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n        \\\"models\\\": [\\n          {\\n            \\\"provider\\\": \\\"openai\\\",\\n            \\\"model\\\": \\\"gpt-4o-mini-transcribe\\\"\\n          }\\n        ]\\n      }\\n    }\\n  },\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_JSTKQWbEED6G8AseZtyJSRUB|fc_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c3346cb6f88191a2b3fb524d50de8e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cmd /c openclaw gateway restart","workdir":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"cmd /c openclaw gateway restart\",\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\"yieldMs\":15000,\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":198,"output":451,"cacheRead":34944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35593,"cost":{"input":0.000495,"output":0.006765,"cacheRead":0.008735999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774400606953,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c334634f508191804582cba8ee813a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4330c0c","parentId":"48ad74cd","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:03:37.488Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_mExoWXLeS4bEmLZyGOGkccuS|fc_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c3346cb6e88191a3fe3df1104ced19","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 112       \"search\": {\n 113         \"enabled\": true,\n 114         \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\"\n 115       }\n+116     },\n+117     \"media\": {\n+118       \"audio\": {\n+119         \"enabled\": true,\n+120         \"models\": [\n+121           {\n+122             \"provider\": \"openai\",\n+123             \"model\": \"gpt-4o-mini-transcribe\"\n+124           }\n+125         ]\n+126       }\n 116     }\n 117   },\n 118   \"bindings\": [\n 119     {\n     ...","firstChangedLine":116},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774400617487}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d8b7e9c","parentId":"f4330c0c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:07:32.953Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3A089E1306F796F44BA0\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"3EB0742D696BBE9E2A60F2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"75806961324068@lid\",\n  \"body\": \"Revisé. Diagnóstico claro:\\n\\n*Sí recibo audios, pero no tienes activada la transcripción de audio en OpenClaw.*\\n\\n*Qué encontré*\\n- WhatsApp está *OK* y el canal *sí entrega media*.\\n- Tus audios entran como `.ogg`, o sea el inbound funciona.\\n- En tu `openclaw.json` *no existe configuración* de `tools.media.audio`.\\n- La doc local de OpenClaw dice que para transcribir audios hay que:\\n- dejar *auto-detección* funcionando, o\\n- configurar explícitamente `tools.media.audio.models`\\n\\n*El detalle importante*\\nSegún la doc, si no configuras nada, OpenClaw intenta auto-detectar transcripción con este orden:\\n1. CLIs locales (`whisper`, `whisper-cli`, `sherpa-onnx-offline`)\\n2. Gemini CLI\\n3. providers (OpenAI, Groq, Deepgram, Google)\\n\\nComo aquí tus audios llegaron *sin transcript*, lo más probable es una de estas:\\n- no hay ningún motor STT instalado localmente\\n- no hay provider STT disponible para ese flujo\\n- o la auto-detección no está encontrando nada usable\\n\\n*Mi conclusión*\\nLa capa rota no es WhatsApp.\\nLa capa faltante es *STT / audio understanding*.\\n\\n*Lo que te recomiendo*\\nLa forma más limpia es activar esto explícitamente en config con OpenAI transcribe.\\n\\nEjemplo recomendado:\\n```json\\n{\\n\\\"tools\\\": {\\n\\\"media\\\": {\\n\\\"audio\\\": {\\n\\\"enabled\\\": true,\\n\\\"models\\\": [\\n{ \\\"provider\\\": \\\"openai\\\", \\\"model\\\": \\\"gpt-4o-mini-transcribe\\\" }\\n]\\n}\\n}\\n}\\n}\\n```\\n\\n*Qué gano con eso*\\n- tus voice notes se transcriben\\n- el transcript entra como texto al agente\\n- incluso podrían disparar comandos si hablas en audio\\n\\n*Siguiente paso*\\nSi quieres, hago yo mismo esto:\\n1. respaldo tu `openclaw.json`\\n2. le agrego `tools.media.audio`\\n3. te digo si hace falta reiniciar gateway\\n4. probamos con otro audio\\n\\nYo haría eso ya.\"\n}\n```\n\nLo hiciste ?"}],"timestamp":1774400852945}}
