{"type":"message","id":"dcaa3bcb","parentId":"2a8f0cab","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:07:49.052Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Sí: **la config ya quedó puesta**.\n\nConfirmado:\n- `openclaw.json` ya tiene:\n  - `tools.media.audio.enabled: true`\n  - modelo `openai / gpt-4o-mini-transcribe`\n\nLo único que **no pude confirmar limpio** fue el restart, porque ese comando devolvió una salida rara y no un “restart ok” explícito.\n\nPero el gateway **sí aparece corriendo** ahora mismo con la misma config de `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`.\n\n**Mi lectura práctica:**\n- el cambio **sí quedó guardado**\n- lo que falta es **probar con otro audio**\n- si no transcribe todavía, entonces hago un **restart más controlado** y reviso logs\n\nMándame un audio corto de prueba y vemos si ya entra con transcript.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c3356488808191abdbd1dc90450056\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1548,"output":180,"cacheRead":36352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38080,"cost":{"input":0.00387,"output":0.0027,"cacheRead":0.009087999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015658}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774400861369,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c335626d1881919fe041eca92ac32f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"62d3a82f","parentId":"dcaa3bcb","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:08:02.537Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\e60b1823-06cc-445b-8e5a-bab234f5968d.ogg (audio/ogg; codecs=opus)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3A91E3008DF48432F887\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\n<media:audio>"}],"timestamp":1774400882533}}
{"type":"message","id":"2bf8f998","parentId":"62d3a82f","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:08:06.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Todavía me llegó como **audio bruto**, no como texto transcrito.\n\nEso sugiere una de dos:\n- el gateway **no recargó** esa parte aún\n- o falta una credencial/ruta efectiva para que `openai` transcribe funcione en este flujo\n\nSiguiente movimiento correcto: **reinicio controlado + revisar logs del gateway** para ver si está intentando transcribir y por qué falla.\n\nSi quieres, hago eso ahora y te saco la causa exacta.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c335773ac0819187d869b9ce86bbc0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2885,"output":110,"cacheRead":35456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38451,"cost":{"input":0.0072125,"output":0.00165,"cacheRead":0.008864,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0177265}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774400882537,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33576814c8191bbc567080b632c71"}}
