{"type":"message","id":"29490b5b","parentId":"17ceae56","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:23:43.748Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\cbaa2418-1f85-436c-a7ef-abcbfc2efe41.ogg (audio/ogg; codecs=opus)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3A587018E7C7B81EF0D3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\n<media:audio>"}],"timestamp":1774401823744}}
{"type":"message","id":"97b0afcf","parentId":"29490b5b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:23:50.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Todavía me llegó como **audio**, no como transcript visible.\n\nPero ojo: eso **no prueba solo** que siga roto, porque OpenClaw puede usar la transcripción internamente sin “mostrármela” literal en el cuerpo del mensaje.\n\nLa prueba real ahora es esta:\n- si quieres, reviso el **log exacto** de esta última nota de voz\n- ahí se ve si:\n  1. Whisper corrió\n  2. falló\n  3. o transcribió pero no hizo echo del transcript\n\nMi lectura honesta:\n- antes no había motor\n- ahora **sí hay motor instalado**\n- falta confirmar si el flujo de OpenClaw está **leyendo bien la salida de Whisper**\n\nSi quieres, hago esa verificación final y lo dejo cerrado.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c339267a5c8191a7ccefbbc806fc76\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":82729,"output":174,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82903,"cost":{"input":0.20682250000000002,"output":0.00261,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.20943250000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774401823748,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33924094881919fea2182bce4e5ff"}}
