{"type":"message","id":"77355f17","parentId":"9fa69003","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:25:10.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Revisé y encontré esto:\n\n- **No aparece ningún rastro de transcripción ejecutándose** en el log de ese último audio.\n- Sí aparece:\n  - el audio entrando\n  - el gateway recibiéndolo\n  - la config de `tools.media.audio.models` recargándose\n- Pero **no aparece**:\n  - `Transcript`\n  - `whisper`\n  - `echoTranscript`\n  - ni un intento claro de procesamiento de audio\n\n**Traducción práctica**\nOpenClaw **está viendo el audio**, pero **no está disparando la fase de transcripción** como esperábamos.\n\nEntonces hice un ajuste adicional:\n- activé `echoTranscript`\n- le puse formato visible:\n  - `📝 {transcript}`\n- forcé parámetros más claros para Whisper:\n  - `--task transcribe`\n  - `--language es`\n  - `--output_format txt`\n\nEso deja la siguiente prueba mucho más binaria:\n- si transcribe, **te debe mandar el transcript visible**\n- si no manda nada, sabemos que el problema ya no es Whisper sino **cómo OpenClaw está invocando o aceptando el CLI**\n\n**Dónde estamos**\n- WhatsApp inbound: ✅\n- Whisper instalado: ✅\n- config local apuntando al binario real: ✅\n- eco de transcript activado: ✅\n- transcripción ocurriendo en runtime: **todavía no confirmada**\n\n**Siguiente paso**\nMándame **un último audio corto**.\n\nSi ahora sale `📝 ...`, quedó.\nSi no sale, ya toca una corrección más quirúrgica del contrato CLI que OpenClaw espera para `tools.media.audio`.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33972276c8191b72a72c7ac1d346a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":28504,"output":356,"cacheRead":107392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136252,"cost":{"input":0.07126,"output":0.00534,"cacheRead":0.026848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.103448}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774401900495,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33970a71481919fd9f7acefdae6d8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e4a0ae5","parentId":"77355f17","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:26:12.328Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\5029fe42-3d7e-4969-9ece-364d7bbfc3e9.ogg (audio/ogg; codecs=opus)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3AEC533F9D25EFDFFD3B\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\n<media:audio>"}],"timestamp":1774401972325}}
{"type":"message","id":"615a554b","parentId":"6e4a0ae5","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:26:21.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Sigue sin aparecer transcript visible.\n\nYa con esto la conclusión cambia: **no es solo configuración superficial**.  \nHay un desacople entre **cómo OpenClaw espera consumir el CLI** y **cómo Whisper está devolviendo/gestionando la salida** en Windows.\n\n**Lo bueno**\n- ya aislamos bastante:\n  - audio entra\n  - config recarga\n  - Whisper está instalado\n\n**Lo que falta**\n- adaptar el método para que OpenClaw realmente **capture el texto transcrito**\n\nLas dos rutas técnicas que quedan son:\n\n1. **envolver Whisper con un script puente**\n   - recibe `{{MediaPath}}`\n   - ejecuta Whisper\n   - lee el `.txt`\n   - imprime solo texto limpio a stdout  \n   Esta es probablemente la solución más robusta.\n\n2. **revisar si OpenClaw espera archivo de salida en ruta específica**\n   - menos probable con este CLI, pero hay que validarlo\n\nMi recomendación ya no es seguir tirando audios a ciegas.  \nAhora toca hacer el **puente limpio** y dejarlo bien.\n\nSi quieres, hago eso ya:\n- te creo un script local de transcripción\n- cambio `openclaw.json` para usarlo\n- y hacemos una última prueba seria","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c339bb1fd08191a583dda9594ac207\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":441,"output":270,"cacheRead":136064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136775,"cost":{"input":0.0011025000000000002,"output":0.00405,"cacheRead":0.034016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.039168499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774401972329,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c339b88b048191a746b96423d3d1a4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c7735b11","parentId":"615a554b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:26:52.660Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3AABE83F501D0707CFA3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\nDe una"}],"timestamp":1774402012657}}
{"type":"message","id":"6391a318","parentId":"c7735b11","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:27:11.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Voy a crear un script puente para Whisper que siempre imprima el transcript limpio a stdout, luego apunto OpenClaw a ese script.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c339e20e6881918d1dc686e96c58f4\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_IT66h3qHCSSnkNMIxdKNUfiX|fc_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c339f246a081918195768714260c21","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\whisper-bridge.py","content":"import argparse\nimport os\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nimport tempfile\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nWHISPER_EXE = r\"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\AppData\\Local\\Python\\pythoncore-3.14-64\\Scripts\\whisper.exe\"\n\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n    parser.add_argument(\"media_path\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--model\", default=\"base\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--language\", default=\"es\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    media = Path(args.media_path)\n    if not media.exists():\n        print(f\"media not found: {media}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        sys.exit(2)\n\n    with tempfile.TemporaryDirectory(prefix=\"whisper-bridge-\") as td:\n        outdir = Path(td)\n        cmd = [\n            WHISPER_EXE,\n            str(media),\n            \"--model\", args.model,\n            \"--task\", \"transcribe\",\n            \"--language\", args.language,\n            \"--output_format\", \"txt\",\n            \"--output_dir\", str(outdir),\n            \"--fp16\", \"False\",\n        ]\n        proc = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, encoding=\"utf-8\", errors=\"replace\")\n        txt_path = outdir / f\"{media.stem}.txt\"\n        if proc.returncode != 0:\n            err = (proc.stderr or proc.stdout or \"whisper failed\").strip()\n            print(err, file=sys.stderr)\n            sys.exit(proc.returncode)\n        if not txt_path.exists():\n            print(\"transcript file not produced\", file=sys.stderr)\n            sys.exit(3)\n        text = txt_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\", errors=\"replace\").strip()\n        print(text)\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\scripts\\\\whisper-bridge.py\",\"content\":\"import argparse\\nimport os\\nimport subprocess\\nimport sys\\nimport tempfile\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\n\\nWHISPER_EXE = r\\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Python\\\\pythoncore-3.14-64\\\\Scripts\\\\whisper.exe\\\"\\n\\n\\ndef main():\\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser()\\n    parser.add_argument(\\\"media_path\\\")\\n    parser.add_argument(\\\"--model\\\", default=\\\"base\\\")\\n    parser.add_argument(\\\"--language\\\", default=\\\"es\\\")\\n    args = parser.parse_args()\\n\\n    media = Path(args.media_path)\\n    if not media.exists():\\n        print(f\\\"media not found: {media}\\\", file=sys.stderr)\\n        sys.exit(2)\\n\\n    with tempfile.TemporaryDirectory(prefix=\\\"whisper-bridge-\\\") as td:\\n        outdir = Path(td)\\n        cmd = [\\n            WHISPER_EXE,\\n            str(media),\\n            \\\"--model\\\", args.model,\\n            \\\"--task\\\", \\\"transcribe\\\",\\n            \\\"--language\\\", args.language,\\n            \\\"--output_format\\\", \\\"txt\\\",\\n            \\\"--output_dir\\\", str(outdir),\\n            \\\"--fp16\\\", \\\"False\\\",\\n        ]\\n        proc = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\", errors=\\\"replace\\\")\\n        txt_path = outdir / f\\\"{media.stem}.txt\\\"\\n        if proc.returncode != 0:\\n            err = (proc.stderr or proc.stdout or \\\"whisper failed\\\").strip()\\n            print(err, file=sys.stderr)\\n            sys.exit(proc.returncode)\\n        if not txt_path.exists():\\n            print(\\\"transcript file not produced\\\", file=sys.stderr)\\n            sys.exit(3)\\n        text = txt_path.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\", errors=\\\"replace\\\").strip()\\n        print(text)\\n\\n\\nif __name__ == \\\"__main__\\\":\\n    main()\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4JKWdS19avv78vdgOl4qpkLk|fc_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c339f2477c8191b9b0aa6ccbd765e2","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","old_string":"          {\n            \"type\": \"cli\",\n            \"command\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Python\\\\pythoncore-3.14-64\\\\Scripts\\\\whisper.exe\",\n            \"args\": [\n              \"--model\",\n              \"base\",\n              \"--task\",\n              \"transcribe\",\n              \"--language\",\n              \"es\",\n              \"--output_format\",\n              \"txt\",\n              \"{{MediaPath}}\"\n            ],\n            \"timeoutSeconds\": 180\n          }","new_string":"          {\n            \"type\": \"cli\",\n            \"command\": \"python\",\n            \"args\": [\n              \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\scripts\\\\whisper-bridge.py\",\n              \"{{MediaPath}}\",\n              \"--model\",\n              \"base\",\n              \"--language\",\n              \"es\"\n            ],\n            \"timeoutSeconds\": 180\n          }"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\openclaw.json\",\"old_string\":\"          {\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"cli\\\",\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\Gustavo\\\\\\\\AppData\\\\\\\\Local\\\\\\\\Python\\\\\\\\pythoncore-3.14-64\\\\\\\\Scripts\\\\\\\\whisper.exe\\\",\\n            \\\"args\\\": [\\n              \\\"--model\\\",\\n              \\\"base\\\",\\n              \\\"--task\\\",\\n              \\\"transcribe\\\",\\n              \\\"--language\\\",\\n              \\\"es\\\",\\n              \