{"type":"message","id":"1cefb58f","parentId":"261d83d4","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:29:14.819Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Perfecto.\n\nEntonces estamos así:\n\n- **causa raíz encontrada:** falta **ffmpeg**\n- **Whisper local:** ya instalado\n- **script puente:** ya creado\n- **config de OpenClaw:** ya apuntando a la ruta correcta\n\nLo único pendiente para cerrar esto es:\n- instalar `ffmpeg`\n- dejarlo en `PATH`\n- probar un último audio\n\nCuando quieras, sigo con eso y te lo dejo andando.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33a6bcc8081918d21ab6c392ae357\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":233,"output":100,"cacheRead":139392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139725,"cost":{"input":0.0005825,"output":0.0015,"cacheRead":0.034848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0369305}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774402146501,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33a66b5388191a865ea6beeb76726"}}
