{"type":"message","id":"ecf5c170","parentId":"c3e235a7","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:32:27.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo. Ya te lo dejé en config.\n\nHice esto:\n- habilité `tools.elevated.enabled`\n- permití elevación **solo** para tu número en WhatsApp:\n  - `+573183718246`\n\nAhora falta que OpenClaw **tome ese cambio**.  \nDependiendo de esa parte del runtime, puede requerir **reload** o **restart** del gateway.\n\n**Siguiente paso**\nDime:\n- **“reintenta”**\n\ny pruebo de nuevo la instalación de `ffmpeg`.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33b2c01e881918f8a1f8596fe1126\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":164,"output":121,"cacheRead":141696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141981,"cost":{"input":0.00041000000000000005,"output":0.001815,"cacheRead":0.035424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.037648999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774402342585,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c33b2ac9c081919123902f2dc14c1e"}}
