{"type":"message","id":"d85466c0","parentId":"7e43ee80","timestamp":"2026-03-25T02:02:04.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] En tu PC haz esto, en este orden:\n\n1. **Instala ffmpeg**\n```powershell\nwinget install --id Gyan.FFmpeg --accept-source-agreements --accept-package-agreements\n```\n\n2. **Verifica que quedó**\n```powershell\nffmpeg -version\n```\n\n3. **Prueba el bridge directo**\n```powershell\npython C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\whisper-bridge.py C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\21409a04-c777-409c-9428-789e1e674de4.ogg --model base --language es\n```\n\n**Qué debería pasar**\n- si `ffmpeg` quedó bien, el paso 2 muestra versión\n- si el bridge quedó bien, el paso 3 te imprime el texto del audio\n\n**Si algo falla**\npégame aquí:\n- la salida de `ffmpeg -version`\n- y la salida completa del comando del bridge\n\nCon eso te digo el siguiente ajuste exacto.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c3421ba9ec8191b90644e593db5d16\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":143935,"output":235,"cacheRead":3584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147754,"cost":{"input":0.35983750000000003,"output":0.003525,"cacheRead":0.000896,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.36425850000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774404114115,"responseId":"resp_0c4adb51b76bd9770169c34217942081919d5b9e02c1d7ccac"}}
